				<wikidot:authorName>Rokonuxa</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1545417</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>This feels like the info dump by a scientist in of one of those supernatural global monster catastrophe-mangas.</p> <p>Next up is some group of kids living a good life, then waking up to find out that their neighborhood is between the toes of some giant reptilian looking footprint, which is actually only revealed after ~40 chapters when they finally make it through the smaller (10 meter scale) monsters to a helicopter which of course crashes within minutes.</p> <p>I like it. +1</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
